.spec/e2e-coordinator-config-schema.md:379:| `E2E_ARTIFACTS_DIR` | Peer artifact directory. |
.spec/e2e-coordinator-config-schema.md:381:| `E2E_PEER_LISTEN_PORT` | Peer listener port. Present only when the peer launch plan has `connection`. |
