   146
   147	Required object.
   148
   149	| Field | Type | Required | Description |
   150	| --- | --- | --- | --- |
   151	| `root` | path template | yes | Run artifact root. Supports `${sessionId}` and `${profileName}`. |
   152	| `keepSuccessfulRuns` | bool | no | Whether successful run artifacts are preserved. Default: `true`. |
   153	| `writeResolvedConfig` | bool | no | Write fully resolved config into artifacts. Default: `true`. |
   154	| `writeEventLog` | bool | no | Write append-only event log. Default: `true`. |
   155	| `writeReceipts` | bool | no | Write publish and delivery receipts. Default: `true`. |
   156	| `collectXcresults` | bool | no | Copy or link peer `.xcresult` bundles. Default: `true` for `xctest` peers. |
   157	| `collectScreenshots` | bool | no | Extract screenshots when available. Default: `true`. |
